    public class TreeNode
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Represents an generic tree node in the CONIKS binary Merkle prefix tree.

      • clone

        public TreeNode clone(TreeNode parent,
             long ep0,
             long ep1)
        Cloning is not supported by generic TreeNodes, only by their sub classes as these specify the more specific data that needs to be duplicated when rebuilding the CONIKS Merkle tree. Therefore each sub class of TreeNode must specify its own cloning function.
        Throws:
        An - UnsupportedOperationException.
